it.eng.spagobi.meta.model.physical
Interface PhysicalModel

All Superinterfaces:
ModelObject
All Known Implementing Classes:
PhysicalModelImpl
public interface PhysicalModel
extends ModelObject

A representation of the model object 'Physical Model'.

The following features are supported:

  • Database Name
  • Database Version
  • Catalog
  • Schema
  • Parent Model
  • Tables
  • Primary Keys
  • Foreign Keys

See Also:
PhysicalModelPackage.getPhysicalModel()
